title: SOUTHIE 4 BED 1.5 BATH AVAILABLE NOW!
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 236999071', 'Rent: $3,700 / Month', 'Beds: 4', 'Bath: 1.5', 'Available Date: 06/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats Only', 'Parking:: no parking', 'Available for Immediate Move-in!!!', "This Second Floor 4 Bedroom with 1.5 Bathrooms in South Boston's Polish Triangle Features Ensuite Laundry Plus a Stainless Steel, Eat-in Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Breakfast Bar, Electric Stove, Full Refrigerator, Dishwasher, and Microwave.", 'Natural Hardwood Floors are Laid Throughout Including in the Kitchen and in the Second Largest Bedroom with Parquet Flooring and Custom-Built Closet.', 'All Lockable Bedrooms are Graced with Ceiling Fans, and the Main Bedroom Offers a Spacious Closet with Sliding Mirror Door.', 'A Private, Rear-Facing Porch is Also On Deck, and Plenty of Resident On-Street Parking Can be Found Outside.', 'Just Two Blocks From Andrew Station Redline with Basketball/Tennis Courts Conveniently Situated in the Rear of this Mixed-Use Building.', 'Placed Near Great Local Restaurants, Pubs, Beaches, and Shops at South Bay Mall; and Super Accessible to I-93 N-S.', 'Virtual tour available upon request!!']
